# .gitignore — track PRODUCTS (derived knowledge), ignore INPUTS (regenerable).
# Policy source: 基调-D2 (only track products; inputs stay local).

# --- inputs / intermediates (regenerable, local-only) ---
# Original source PDFs (frozen input after MD conversion; MD-only contract).
corpus/**/*.pdf
# Full MinerU image dumps (the curated subset is copied into vault figures/).
corpus/**/images/
# MinerU structured intermediate.
corpus/**/content_list.json
# MinerU per-paper work dir (paper.md + intermediates); the canonical {ID}.md
# product is written at the paper-dir root, not inside mineru/.
corpus/**/mineru/

# Citation-lookup cache + secrets.
.cache/
.env

# --- python / tooling ---
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# CodeGraph index (per-machine, regenerable tooling state)
.codegraph/

# Transient clone area (analysis-D2: clone-then-delete; pointers kept in ai_package).
/tmp/paper-repos/

# NOTE: everything else is tracked on purpose — *.md knowledge products,
# person_vault/, ai_package/, _ledger/, landscapes/, config/, .md_contract.json,
# and curated branch1 figures. Do NOT add blanket ignores for those.

# oh-my-codex review log (scratch, not a product)
/attn_sink/

# --- reference provenance archive (docs/reference/) ---
# The cloned upstream repos we drew from carry their OWN .git and are large;
# they are local-only provenance, not paper-rolling products. Track ONLY the
# hand-written INDEX.md (the manifest: URLs, licenses, what each was used for).
/docs/reference/*
!/docs/reference/INDEX.md

# LS-1 runtime lock (persistent inode; flock state is the lock) — not a product
_ledger/.lock

# /loop scheduler lock (transient session state, not a product)
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Machine-local Claude Code config (per-machine; not shared products).
# NOTE: .claude/settings.json IS tracked on purpose (shared project permissions).
.claude/settings.local.json
.mcp.json

# claude-mem project memory (per-machine SQLite state; not a product)
.claude/mem.db*

# macOS 噪声
.DS_Store

# git worktree 检出(根目录 .worktrees/,惯例位置)
/.worktrees/

# 失败现场=本地诊断 scratch，不是产物（ADR-0007）。保留 .gitkeep 占位。
/_failed/*
!/_failed/.gitkeep
